OL,3,CCuba hit by third nationwide blackout
OL,4,Cthis month amid US energy blockade
OL,6,FCuba's power grid collapsed again on
OL,7,FSaturday leaving the country without
OL,8,Felectricity for a third time in March.
OL,10,FThe Cuban Electric Union said the
OL,11,Fblackout was caused by a failure of a
OL,12,Fgenerating unit at the Nuevitas
OL,13,Fthermoelectric plant in Camaguey
OL,14,Fprovince.
OL,16,FIt was the second blackout in the past
OL,17,Fweek and the third this month, with
OL,18,FCuba blaming the crisis partly on a US
OL,19,Fenergy blockade.
OL,26,@uD@^xz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
