OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774303863
OL,3,CCuba hit by third nationwide blackout
OL,4,Cthis month amid US energy blockade
OL,6,FThrough military action in Venezuela
OL,7,Fand threats of tariffs on Mexico,
OL,8,FTrump has prevented oil from entering
OL,9,Fthe island, crippling an economy
OL,10,Falready hamstrung by the communist
OL,11,Fgovernment's own disastrous limits on
OL,12,Fprivate industry.
OL,14,FTrump's secretary of state, Marco
OL,15,FRubio, a Cuban American and a fierce
OL,16,Fcritic of the island's leadership, is
OL,17,Fleading negotiations with Havana. He
OL,18,Fhas been preparing his entire
OL,19,Fprofessional life for this moment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
