OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774303863
OL,3,CCuba hit by third nationwide blackout
OL,4,Cthis month amid US energy blockade
OL,6,FAfter weeks of rumours and leaks in
OL,7,FWashington, Cuba confirmed
OL,8,Fnegotiations were being held.
OL,10,FThe government released 51 prisoners,
OL,11,Fsome of them jailed for protesting
OL,12,Fagainst the administration, and
OL,13,Fannounced long-awaited, if still
OL,14,Flimited in scope, reforms that would
OL,15,Fallow Cubans living abroad to invest
OL,16,Fon the island.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
