OL,3,CCuba hit by third nationwide blackout
OL,4,Cthis month amid US energy blockade
OL,6,F"Whenever we have been in tense
OL,7,Fsituations in relations with the
OL,8,FUnited States, efforts have been made
OL,9,Fto find channels for dialogue," said
OL,10,FCuban President Miguel Diaz-Canel,
OL,11,Falthough recent remarks by US
OL,12,FPresident Donald Trump cast doubt on
OL,13,Fan amicable resolution.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
