OL,3,CCuba hit by third nationwide blackout
OL,4,Cthis month amid US energy blockade
OL,6,FThe Cuban government soon fired back
OL,7,Fat Trump's assertions, with Diaz-Canel
OL,8,Fposting on X: "In the face of the
OL,9,Fworst scenario, Cuba is accompanied by
OL,10,Fa certainty: any external aggressor
OL,11,Fwill clash with an impregnable
OL,12,Fresistance."
OL,14,FLetting the US pick who leads the
OL,15,Fisland was tantamount to surrender and
OL,16,Fwould not be considered, officials
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@pD@OOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
