OL,3,CCuba hit by third nationwide blackout
OL,4,Cthis month amid US energy blockade
OL,6,F"Neither the president nor the
OL,7,Fposition of any leader in Cuba is up
OL,8,Ffor negotiation with the United
OL,9,FStates," Cuba's top diplomat for US
OL,10,Faffairs, Carlos Fernandez De Cossio,
OL,11,Ftold reporters in Havana on Friday.
OL,13,FTrump's threats and the oil blockade
OL,14,Fseem to have united Cuban officials
OL,15,Fand supporters of the government at
OL,16,Fthe same time his administration was
OL,17,Ftrying to splinter its inner circle.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]rD@Urp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
