OL,3,CCuba hit by third nationwide blackout
OL,4,Cthis month amid US energy blockade
OL,6,F"The (Cuban) government's claim that
OL,7,Fit's the US embargo that's at fault
OL,8,Fwas wearing a little thin, because
OL,9,Fthey've been making that argument for
OL,10,Fmany, many years," William LeoGrande,
OL,11,Fa professor at American University,
OL,12,Ftold CNN.
OL,14,F"It's true, of course, that the US
OL,15,Feconomic embargo does hamper the Cuban
OL,16,Feconomy tremendously, but people were
OL,17,Fbeginning to blame the government's
OL,18,Fmistakes."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@RO]vD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
