OL,3,CCuba hit by third nationwide blackout
OL,4,Cthis month amid US energy blockade
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe Cuban strategy appears to be keep
OL,12,Ftalking to buy time, perhaps even
OL,13,Funtil the US midterm elections in
OL,14,FNovember when the Democrats could
OL,15,Fregain Congress.
OL,17,FIt's not clear how much time they
OL,18,Freally have, considering both
OL,19,FVenezuela and Iran were in discussions
OL,20,Fwith the US when Trump ordered attacks
OL,21,Fon those countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
