OL,3,CCuba hit by third nationwide blackout
OL,4,Cthis month amid US energy blockade
OL,6,FThere are also reports that the Trump
OL,7,Fadministration may indict former Cuban
OL,8,Fleader Raul Castro ` who still wields
OL,9,Fultimate power on the island ` for his
OL,10,Frole in the shooting down of a plane
OL,11,Foperated by American activist group
OL,12,FBrothers to the Rescue in 1996.
OL,14,FCastro could also be indicted on
OL,15,Fdecades-old allegations of involvement
OL,16,Fin drug trafficking which the Cuban
OL,17,Fgovernment has long denied.
OL,19,FAny US charges against Castro, 94,
OL,20,Fwould likely kill off any chance of a
OL,21,Fdiplomatic solution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
